div.div:
The three tables involved in creating the many-to-many relationship between
the Books table and the Authors table. There used a many-to-many relationship because books
can have many authors, and authors may have written many books. The extra feature
needed here is the Order value, because the order in which authors are listed in a book
matters, so there used the Order value to display the authors in the correct sequence.
